&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weeks 2–4:&lt;/strong&gt; Hands-on internal training focused on Appian development, consulting methodologies, Agile practices, and professional skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Throughout the program, you&#39;ll receive mentorship from experienced Appian professionals while building the foundation needed to launch your consulting career.&lt;/p&gt;
